(BranchPredictor, decodeWidth).explanation: Branch predictor and decode width are independent architectural parameters that operate at different pipeline stages and do not directly influence each other;

(BranchPredictor, numRCQEntries).explanation: Branch predictor functionality and the number of reorder completion queue entries are independent design parameters that serve different purposes in the processor pipeline;

(BranchPredictor, power).explanation: Branch predictor complexity and accuracy directly affect power consumption through increased transistor count, switching activity, and prediction table accesses;
